    {
      "type": "patchouli:text",
      "text": "The $(l:beneath)Beneath$() hosts its own unique selection of wild fruits, which have adapted to the extreme conditions underground. Wild fruits can be cultivated in all the same ways as regular $(l:the_world/wild_fruits)wild fruits$() in the Overworld."
